body:
And no, I&#039;m not going to say &quot;Just delete it DURHUR&quot;

Devourer is supposed to be bought early, be useless early, and become monstrous late. However, the current one gives Attack Speed worth much more than it costs. Now, how would you nerf this, while still keeping the identity of being very strong late game for on-hit effects? Make the Attack Speed scale with Devourer stacks. For example, every 3 stacks of Devourer, you get 5 Attack Speed. That would add up to 50% at Sated. 

Yeah. That&#039;s it. There you go. You can upvote and comment now.
